<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="ko">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <title>1PY Review</title>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/bootstrap-theme.min.css" />
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style_review.css" />
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery.easings.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery.slimscroll.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery.fullPage.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">창업신청</h4>
      </div>
      <form action="/review" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form-horizontal">
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="basic-addon1">이름</span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="이름" id="username_input" name="name">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="basic-addon1">장소</span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="장소" id="location_input" name="location">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-addon" id="basic-addon1">제목</span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="제목" id="title_input" name="title">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="file" name="img" size="20">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <textarea class="form-control" id="text_input" name="content" rows="10"></textarea>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        <input type="submit" name="Submit" value="신청" class="btn btn-primary">
      </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<nav class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="navbar-header">
            <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navbar">
            <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            </button>
            <a class="navbar-brand"><div id="logo"></div></a>
        </div>
        <div id="navbar" class="navbar-collapse collapse">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                <li><a href="#" id="prev">홈</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" id="write">글쓰기</a></li>
            <!-- <li><a href="#">Dashboard</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Settings</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Profile</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Help</a></li> -->
            </ul>
        <!-- <form class="navbar-form navbar-right">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Search...">
        </form> -->
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="header">
  <div class="txt">
    <div class="txt-l">DISCOVER YOUNGS</div>
    <div class="txt-m">1PY는 젊은 창업가와 실버 투자자가 함께하는 다양한 솔루션을 제공합니다.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="article">
  <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <% for(var i=0; i<data.length; i++) {%>
                <div class="page-header">
                  <h4> <%= data[i].title %> </h4>
                </div>
                <div class="content col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                    <div class="thumbnail">
                        <img src="<%= data[i].img %>" alt="<%= data[i].title %>">
                        <div class="caption">
                            <h4></h4>
                            <p><%= data[i].content %></p>
                            <p class="etc">
                                <%= data[i].name %><br>
                                <%= data[i].date %><br>
                                <%= data[i].location %>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    <div class="copyright">
        (주)한평의꿈   대표: 김민순 주소: 서울특별시 은평구 갈현로37길 29-5 사업자등록번호: 574-34-00020 <b>대표번호: 1800-0713</b><br>
        Copyright© 1py Inc. All rights reserved.
    </div>
    <div class="footer-image"></div>
</div>  

<script>
    $('#logo').on('click', function() {
        //var url = window.location.pathname;
        window.location.href = '/review';
    });
    
    $('#prev').on('click', function(e){
        e.preventDefault();
        var url = window.location.origin;
        window.location.href = url;
        return false;
    });

    $('#write').on('click', function(e){
        e.preventDefault();
        $('#myModal').modal();
    })
</script>

</body>
</html>
